data.text:
Rhoda Name Popularity

At NamesLook, the name Rhoda is recorded 5,176 times globally, ranking it as the 9,811th most common name worldwide.

Rhoda is most prevalent in Nigeria, with 1,526 occurrences, making it the 882th most popular name in the country.
